XSGD, developed by StraitsX, is a regulated stablecoin pegged 1:1 to the Singapore Dollar (SGD). Launched with a focus on regional interoperability, XSGD is designed to revolutionize cross-border payments and DeFi applications in Southeast Asia. It is fully backed by reserve assets held by StraitsX, ensuring redeemability at par value, and complies with Singaporeâ€™s forthcoming Single Currency Stablecoin regulatory framework. Available on multiple blockchains, including Ethereum and now Base, XSGD offers fast settlements, FX flexibility, and programmable use cases, making it a versatile tool for both institutional and retail users.

